    "video_length": "PT7M22S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Trial is kinda like violin", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We more or less know that you should not", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "play with your feet to avoid false notes", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But from here to Mozart there\u2019s a huge gap", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "especially when seeing what virtuosi are able to do", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on board of these dwarf bikes without saddles", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the whole Moto Journal team went back to school", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Theoretical 101 first with the visit", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of the incredible off-road museum of Joel Corroy", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The \u201cTrail 70\u201d boss from Vesoul", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We went back to the times of grandpa\u2019s trial ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Where they mounted Greeves, lacking other", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Merlin, Matchless, AJS, Montesa, Bultaco\u2026", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and of course JCM", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A bike made here by the Joel Corroy and his own hands", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "A trial bike that climbed the 746 steps from", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the first two floors of the Eiffel Tower in 1983", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Which is making us feel old though", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But at Mojo Journal over the benches and history books", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we always preferred the playground", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So let&#39;s get to La Bresse in the Vosges, and practice ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Up there in the mountains the trial school is hiding", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with a whole lot of strange bikes awaiting us", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Two and four strokes, and magnificentdancer suits", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And also the instructors with pretty girls among them", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There\u2019s a position that I like to call \u201cpoop break\u201d", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with shoulders low and bum up", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This position puts a lot of weight on the arms", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you\u2019re looking at the front wheel", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I don\u2019t like school ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "\u2026and that\u2019s really not good", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "\u2026and that\u2019s really not good", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the idea is show-off on the bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At the time you\u2019re tightening it\u2019s the bike that rides you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and then you struggle\u2026like hell", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Trial ? I heard you only need to be legless to be good", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because the only goal is to keep moving forward", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "without setting a foot to the ground", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Easy !", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Except that the ground isn\u2019t flat", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the corners aren\u2019t even straight", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and moreover the ground rises", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Perfect control ! That\u2019s exactly what I wanted to do", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Perfect control ! That\u2019s exactly what I wanted to do", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hoping to see us set at least a foot on the ground", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Trial is kinda like culture: the less you have", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the more you sprawl\u2026", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I remember why I never exercise", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it\u2019s too harsh", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "With a few exceptions trial is a new thing to the MJ boys", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it takes more to daunt us", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as it is said that ridicule never killed anyone\u2026", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look: Jacques, photographer more than trialist", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Expert in grip search too", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "doesn\u2019t seems more at ease on the bike than next to it", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Jacky ! The tire ! You\u2019ll make the whole place burn !", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Jacky get out you\u2019re spoiling the area !", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There\u2019s also those balancing their deficiency with bikes", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "by speaking great things, like Fred", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "more at ease with words than wheels", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I\u2019m not made for off-road I\u2019m an urban guy", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a pavement flower", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "stuffs in the country: no thanks", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Caf\u00e9-racers and company maybe moto-bistrot", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but not affectations as this in the nature", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "otherwise you stare at this landscape", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "magnificent little paradise in the Vosges", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "At last there\u2019s the beginner\u2019s luck", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "look at the chief editor passing this tremendous menhir", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and its 30cm height", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like it was nothing\u2026", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It\u2019s has been a bit easy until now", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I really want it to get harder", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or it will end up with none of us injured otherwise", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "\u2026And then miserably fail at his second try", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This one is for you", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After 2 hours of course", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and a perfect mastering of the leanings", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "footpegs, arms, shoulders, butt", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And with the killer look as well", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was certain now, we were real pros", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even better than the chamois", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we proudly went to an international competition", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s serious business at the Trial Urbain of Carpentras", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with the world elite present we grew scared", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It\u2019s a bit like going from \u201cJeux Interdits\u201d with one string", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to the wild rhythm of \u201chey joe\u201d by Jimmy Hendrix", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we simply watched the pros", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So how does the Trial Urbain works ?", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There\u2019s 6 path to take 3 or 4 times", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There\u2019s one recon run where you can get with the bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but there\u2019s not any point counted", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then there\u2019s 3 laps where they count the points", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And in the end the one with the fewest points that wins", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that\u2019s reverted", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What is a watch useful for in trial ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well we have 1:30 minute for every section", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that\u2019s why I was just setting my own watch", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I need the exact time because after 1:30 m", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we take 1 point of penalty every 10 seconds", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So to avoid this extra points we\u2019re focusing on time", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Trial is not only practiced with a bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but also on foot\u2026a lot", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You need to learn every difficult points", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "estimate the positions and trajectories", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some even clean up stuffs", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Then you have to go, but not alone hey", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because trial is also a love story", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ok not at two on the bike since there&#39;s no saddle", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but with a wing-man following you like your own shadow", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shouting all kind of orders with his headset", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If a complete beginner would certainly manage", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to accomplish a few laps with a Moto GP bike", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "even if not as quickly", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We can\u2019t say much about the Trial Urbain ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When we see that even on foot it isn\u2019t easy", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for the elite everything seems clear", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the placements are a question of millimeters ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and with a good throttle, the gaps are swallowed", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "just as easy as pie", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In front of a stunned public", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There\u2019s the super-focused ones, the anxious", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the determined one and also the showmen", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like the Japanese rider Takahisa Fujinami", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and his four-stroke official Honda", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that is always great, with the sense of the show", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and the public\u2019s respect that he has back", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "simply beautiful", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In a 2 hours spectacle", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "these equilibrists literally amazed us", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I thought we were good after", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a few hours of training\u2026", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a little offended we gave back ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "our ridiculous skin-tight suits", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and wore our classic leathers ", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Farewall fellas !", 
            "dur": 0, 
            "start": 0
        }
